RiskText: I understand that I can lose the money I'm investing
DiversificationText: I understand that it's safer to split money across many investments and asset classes
LimitedTransferText: I understand that it may be difficult to trade and transfer my investments
CancellationText: I understand that I can't cancel a transaction after completion or unwind a trade
Limits: I understand that I can't invest more than my limits allow
Research: I understand that doing research is my own responsibility
